  MetricList, Offset, TimestampColumn, DimensionList, MetricSetFrequency,
  MetricSource)

Arguments

MetricSetArn

[required] The ARN of the dataset to update.

MetricSetDescription

The dataset's description.

MetricList

The metric list.

Offset

After an interval ends, the amount of seconds that the detector waits before importing data. Offset is only supported for S3 and Redshift datasources.

TimestampColumn

The timestamp column.

DimensionList

The dimension list.

MetricSetFrequency

The dataset's interval.

MetricSource

Value

A list with the following syntax:

)
